title: J Lo Looks Better Than Ever in Famous Versace Dress 20 Years Later
text:
J Lo is giving us major nostalgia as she slipped back on that famous Versace dress and walked the runway two decades later.

The 50-year-old stunned on the catwalk while recreating her iconic look during Milan Fashion Week on Friday.

Related:

Jennifer Lopez's Skimpy 'Hustlers' Outfit From Opening Scene Could Fit In The Designer's Hand

OMG!

Holding her head proudly while strutting her stuff during Donatella Versace's show, J Lo has every reason to be confident. SHE JUST BROKE THE INTERNET!!

Last time we saw the "Hustlers" actress wearing this daring dress was February 23, 2000, at the Grammy Awards when she walked the carpet with then-boyfriend Diddy.

Breaking The Internet!

When she rocked this dress nearly two full decades ago, she began "trending" before it was actually a thing.

A lot has changed in J Lo's life since then, but one thing that remains is her excellent body.

The singer looks better than ever after turning the big 5-0 and proved to be rocking an even better 6-pack than 20 years ago.

Strut It, Baby!
description: J Lo is rocking that infamous jungle Versace dress from 20 years ago and looks better than ever!
